[PlyCount "1"]
[GameId "2133654360688683"]

{Black's king is a bit exposed since the f-pawn has advanced to [f5]. How can White play to make use of this long-term advantage?} 14. Qh5 $18 {[%csl Rg8,Rh7][%cal Gg2g4] The queen is going to be a big disturbance in Black's kingside. There's not an immediate threat yet, but Black is under pressure. An idea is to play [g4] next to open up the kingside further.} (14. Qh5 {Also, if Black plays} Neg6 {, then} 15. Nxh7 {is a tactic to remove the defender of the [g6]-knight.}) *

