{White has the opportunity to win material. How can we accomplish this?} 12. Ba3 {[%csl Rf8][%cal Ga3f8]} (12. Bc6 {is fine too:} Rb8 13. Ba3 Re8 14. Bd6 {+- .}) 12... Re8 13. Bc6 {[%csl Ra8][%cal Gc6a8]} Ba6 {Black decides to lose the exchange this way rather than moving the rook to [b8].} ({In case of} 13... Rb8 14. Bd6 {+- , White traps the rook and will win the exchange.}) 14. Bxa8 $18 {After Black recaptures on [a8], we will be ahead an exchange.} *

[Event "Seal the Deal: How to Gain and Convert Middlegame Advantages"]
[Site "?"]
