{Black has just captured our knight on [e5]. How should we recapture in order to gain a space advantage?} 11. dxe5 {[%csl Re5][%cal Ge5f6] Recapturing with the pawn is best. Not only does it attack Black's knight, but our pawn went from [d4] to [e5] which means it crossed into Black's half of the board. This [e5]-pawn now controls squares further in Black's territory and thus restricts their pieces from moving as easily as they would like to.} (11. Rxe5 $2 {Recapturing with the rook not only doesn't give us a space advantage, but it also loses material!} Ne4 {∓ , now our rook is trapped on [e5] and we will lose the exchange.}) 11... Nd7 {[%cal Gd7e5] How should White defend the [e5]-pawn?} 12. Nf3 {It's best to use the knight to defend the pawn. This gets the knight to a more forward and active location while also getting out of the way of the [c1]-bishop so that it can develop.} (12. f4 $6 {keeps the [e5]-pawn safe and solid but does block our [c1]-bishop's diagonal, which makes it more difficult to activate. After} Nc5 13. Bc2 d4 {∞ , Black also gets the chance to advance in the center and open the position a bit, which is good for them.}) 12... a6 13. Bc2 {[%csl Rd5][%cal Gd1d5] White moves the bishop out of the way in order to put pressure on Black's [d5]-pawn. It is a bit awkward to defend in a useful way.} e6 {[%csl Rc8][%cal Gc8b7,Gc8e6] Black uses their e-pawn to defend, but this shuts in their [c8]-bishop and makes it more difficult to activate that piece. Okay, so White has gained the space advantage since our pawn is in Black's half of the board. What to do next? When you have a space advantage there are usually a few things you want to do. First, you want to secure your central space advantage and make it difficult for the opponent to break it down in a good way. Here, White can do this by overprotecting their [e5]-pawn so that it never becomes a target for Black to attack in a meaningful way.} 14. Bf4 $18 {[%csl Ge5] White develops a new piece and reinforces their [e5]-pawn at the same time. They've done a good job of gaining the space advantage and securing it too.} *

