{In this chapter, you will get the chance to look at a variety of positions. These positions will focus on gaining a static, long-term advantage in the first place, with goals including either weakening the opponent's king safety, winning material, acquiring the bishop pair, gaining space, or creating a pawn weakness. Some puzzles will require multiple correct moves in a row.} 1. Z0 *

